title: #92Noon! 10a Hour - Skol to the Bowl/Siny/PJ
description: The hour begins with discussion on our current optimism for the Vikings at the 1-3 mark. Sinykin brings his Sultan of Smug aura to the airwaves for the Border Battle, then PJ Fleck makes his appearance following the win at Purdue!
